      "FIRST RUN: Use node 10 (LoadImage) as source_image; face model is auto-saved via node 13.",
      "REPEAT RUNS: Connect node 14 (ReActorLoadFaceModel) to node 11 face_model input for consistent identity.",
      "FACE QUALITY: GFPGANv1.4 visibility=1.0 for cleanest result; lower to 0.75 to preserve original skin texture.",
      "RTX UPSCALE: Node 21 requires ComfyUI_NVIDIA_RTX_Nodes (Manager -> search RTX -> install ComfyUI_NVIDIA_RTX_Nodes). Skip node 21 if not on RTX GPU.",
      "FLUX GUIDANCE: Klein 9B best at 3.0-4.0 guidance, euler sampler, 20+ steps.",
      "VIDEO FACE SWAP: Route node 12 IMAGE into VHS_LoadVideo + ReActorFaceSwapONVIDEO for per-frame video face swap.",
      "Z IMAGE TURBO VARIANT: Swap CheckpointLoaderSimple (node 1) to z-image-turbo.safetensors for 3s generation on 6GB VRAM."
